  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Strengthening the role of the formal and non-formal education in the prevention of violence against children in Lebanon (Safe to Learn)</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="4">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">INTERNATIONAL ALERT 
